Package: infotan
Type: Package
Title: Infotan package for the search of next public transport crossings at Nantes.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Theo Bouedo
Description: The infotan package provides a suite of functions for accessing public transport information in the city of Nantes. It includes 4 functions. Functions include get_next_transport, which finds the next passes to a given station, is_station, which checks if an entry is a valid station, get_waiting_time, which retrieves the waiting time for a given location code, and find_closest_name, which finds the nearest station name using a string similarity algorithm.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
  stringdist
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
